title: Shell Fleet App

creator: Shell Information Technology International B.V.
descriptionHtml:
Lose the paperwork. Gain control over your fuel costs.

With Shell Fleet App, we’re redefining what is possible for small businesses with up to 10 vehicles. Businesses owners and their drivers can make use of monthly fuel credit on the wide fuel network across the nation.

Shell Fleet App is the simple way to manage all your fleet’s fuel expenses on a single platform, cutting costs and admin. Attain full visibility into spending and allocate a budget for each one of the fuel cards in your account. It’s both secure and seamless.

Simple sign-up. Register for an account and get approved on the same day. Enjoy our transparent pricing and no tie-ins. Reduce your task list with digital VAT-compliant invoices.
descriptionShort: Drive now, Pay later with monthly fuel credit.

title: Shell Fleet App

creator: Shell Information Technology International B.V.
descriptionHtml:
You started your business for a purpose, not for paperwork. So why fritter away all your time on admin when you could focus on your mission?

Shell Fleet App's goal is simple: empower small businesses with up to 10 cars to do work that matters. We offer fleet management on a single digital platform, cutting fuel costs and removing paperwork from the equation entirely.

Drive now, pay later with monthly fuel credit on your fuel card, which grants you access to our vast nationwide network of 3,800 locations. Attain full visibility into spending for each driver. Take control over your fuel costs by allocating a budget for each one of the cards in your account and setting flexible limits over each card.Do it all without paper, cutting down on the time it would take to manage physical receipts.

Take advantage of our same-day sign-in and register for an account within minutes. It's admin made easy.

6 things you can do with the App:

1. Make the most of your monthly credit limit of £3,000
2. Enjoy fuel credit at over 3,800 stations nationwide
3. Enjoy 4p per litre off V-Power & 3p per litre off standard fuels at Shell
4. Receive digital VAT receipts - no more paperwork!
5. Exercise flexible card controls - different spend limits for different drivers? No problem.
6. Buy fuel & car care items

You'll also benefit from:
- A site locator that allows you to search for the nearest station to you
- Automated payments that allow you to pay your bills without lifting a finger
- No hidden costs or tie-ins
- Digital VAT-compliant invoices
- Full visibility into your spending and payments
- The convenience of paying at the pump without leaving your car
- Wifi, coffee, and snacks for your drivers

We're not just going to stop there. Here are some future benefits to look forward to:
- An EV card which will allow you to both refuel a traditional car and charge your electric vehicle.
- A plan to extend the app's services to businesses with 1-30 cars

Using the app and fuel cards is simple and seamless:
1. Download and register for the app.
2. Once your account has been created, provide your payment details.
3. Order your fuel cards.
4. Activate your fuel cards.
5. Perform your first transaction
6. Add new drivers to the app and set credit limits for each of their cards
7. Receive your very first digital invoice

Do less admin and make more impact with our mobile fleet manager, which offers fuel cards, monthly credit limit, and more for businesses with up to 30 vehicles.

You started your business for a purpose, not for paperwork. So why fritter away all your time on admin when you could focus on your mission?

Shell Fleet App's goal is simple: empower small businesses with up to 30* cars to do work that matters. We offer fleet management on a single digital platform, cutting fuel costs and removing paperwork from the equation entirely.

Drive now, pay later with monthly fuel credit on your fuel card, which grants you access to our vast network of locations. Attain full visibility into spending for each driver. Take control over your fuel costs by allocating a budget for each one of the cards in your account and setting flexible limits over each card. Do it all without paper, cutting down on the time it would take to manage physical receipts.

Take advantage of our same-day sign-in and register for an account within minutes. It's admin made easy.

6 things you can do with the App:

1. Make the most of your monthly credit limit
2. Enjoy fuel credit at over a vast network of stations
3. Enjoy exclusive discounts off V-Power & standard fuels at Shell
4. Receive digital receipts - no more paperwork!
5. Exercise flexible card controls - different spend limits for different drivers? No problem.
6. Buy fuel & car care items

You'll also benefit from:
- A site locator that allows you to search for the nearest station to you
- Automated payments that allow you to pay your bills without lifting a finger
- No hidden costs or tie-ins
- Digital invoices
- Full visibility into your spending and payments
- Wifi, coffee, and snacks for your drivers*
- The convenience of paying at the pump without leaving your car**
- A card that enables you to charge your electric vehicle**

*Only available in certain markets. In some markets, you can add up to 10 vehicles
** Only available in certain markets.

Using the app and fuel cards is simple and seamless:
1. Download and register for the app.
2. Once your account has been created, provide your payment details.
3. Order your fuel cards.
4. Activate your fuel cards.
5. Perform your first transaction
6. Add new drivers to the app and set credit limits for each of their cards
7. Receive your very first digital invoice
